                "invention-title": [
                    "Zinc metallurgy energy storage device",
                    "一种锌冶金储能装置"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to the technical field of electrochemistry and novel energy storage, and discloses a zinc metallurgy energy storage device, which seamlessly connects a zinc metallurgy process with a zinc battery technology by introducing a diaphragm design, and realizes integration and optimization. According to the device, the inter-electrode distance of the zinc metallurgy electrode plates is remarkably reduced, the energy efficiency is improved, harmful impurities can be effectively blocked, and the purity and safety of the production process are ensured. Meanwhile, the device also has a sodium ion enrichment function and high-efficiency separation and recovery capability on oxygen and hydrogen, so that the utilization rate of resources and the environmental protection performance are further improved. The metal zinc electrolyzed and deposited by the device can be directly used as a negative electrode material of the zinc-air battery, and the innovative measure thoroughly omits tedious zinc processing, transportation and zinc ion battery manufacturing links, greatly simplifies the production process and reduces the cost. The technology is introduced into a zinc metallurgy factory, so that the production efficiency of the zinc metallurgy factory can be improved, the business of the energy storage field can be directly expanded, and the diversified improvement of the industrial value is realized."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及电化学和新型储能技术领域，公开了一种锌冶金储能装置，通过引入隔膜设计，将锌冶金工艺与锌电池技术无缝衔接，实现了整合优化。该装置不仅显著降低锌冶金电极板的极间距，提高能效，还能有效阻隔有害杂质，确保生产过程的纯净与安全。同时，它还具备钠离子富集功能以及对氧气和氢气的高效分离与回收能力，进一步提升了资源的利用率和环保性能。本装置电解沉积的金属锌可直接用作锌空气电池的负极材料，这一创新举措彻底省去了繁琐的锌加工、运输以及锌离子电池制造环节，极大地简化了生产流程，降低了成本。锌冶金工厂通过引入这一技术，不仅能够提升自身生产效率，更能直接拓展储能领域的业务，实现产业价值的多元化提升。"
                }
            ]
